snippet.title: Ninja Painter Walkthrough
snippet.description:
Ninja Painter is an amusing and colourful arcade game with addicting gameplay. Help the Ninja to master a new and unusual profession for him - the profession of a house painter. Paint the walls in the countryside, in a town and in a megalopolis through 30 levels and try to get all the achievements!

Link - http://www.agame.com/game/ninja-painter.html
